{"tid":2232803,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"廣瀨鈴確診武漢肺炎！新劇進度拉警報","createTime":"2020-10-06T15:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T17:08:19.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd77f98ec5cd8405710e8a7e43a120feb51d67b","tid":2232803,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/3SzdbCtgKtkHEuv2Oy8egVIR2TQ=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MN23NFW3JVBSRDQ45IF2JMIOCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3SzdbCtgKtkHEuv2Oy8egVIR2TQ%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMN23NFW3JVBSRDQ45IF2JMIOCI.jpg&h=5fb42d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22歲日本女星廣瀨鈴今天確診武漢肺炎，粉絲很為她擔心。她在劇組的例行檢查報告確認是陽性，因而立刻隔離治療，確保其他演員的健康。<br />\n<br />\n她其實對防疫很小心，今年1月到超市買東西，全程都有戴口罩，也沒有在超市多停留，沒想到還是確診，也恐會影響新劇的拍攝進度。<br />\n<br />\n出道邁入第7年的廣瀨鈴，曾演過電影《海街日記》，去年和前輩松嶋菜菜子合作《夏空》，據說在讀劇本時，曾被菜菜子ㄉㄧㄤ過，「應該準備好再來」。外型可愛的她，深獲廣告商喜愛、邀約不斷，去年接下共11個廣告，人氣勝過綾瀨遙、「乃木坂46」白石麻衣、齋藤飛鳥的10代言，是廣告女王。（陳穎/綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201006/M3A3KKXUL5H6JIG2XRZQ2HTSTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201006%2FM3A3KKXUL5H6JIG2XRZQ2HTSTI%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=4801e3c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201006%2FM3A3KKXUL5H6JIG2XRZQ2HTSTI%2F&h=321f2825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201006/M3A3KKXUL5H6JIG2XRZQ2HTSTI/</a>"},{"pid":"23a5ef6071289bc4ef9448e0d78653fa4550a54c","tid":2232803,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"去年接下共11個廣告 咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b39200e96e40f1da6298686